              </mrow>
            </msub>
          </mrow>
          <mrow>
            <msub>
              <mrow>
                <mi>τ</mi>
              </mrow>
              <mrow>
                <mi>i</mi>
              </mrow>
            </msub>
          </mrow>
        </mfrac>
      </mrow>
    </mfenced>
  </math>. We then use equation <a href="#x1-10003r5">5</a> to derive their <span class="cmti-10">observable </span>consequences:
</p>
<dl class="description">
  <dt class="description">
    
    <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
