</p>
<p class="indent">
  It would be nice that our theoretical deduction, excluding, like in physical reasoning, the third mathematical possibility as meaningless, were empirically confirmed in large phyla. Conversely it would be also interesting if this
  theoretical derivation leads to the discovery of species where also the third case is realized.
</p>
<h3 class="subsectionHead" id="43--allometry-and-physical-rhythms"><span id="x1-140004e3" class="titlemark">4.3 </span>Allometry and physical rhythms</h3>
<p class="noindent">
  When we consider organisms with different adult masses (
