      <mrow>
        <mi>t</mi>
      </mrow>
      <mo class="MathClass-close">)</mo>
    </mrow>
  </math>
  axis (as far as
  
  <math display="inline" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
    <mi>f</mi>
  </math> is concerned) whereas the physical rhythm modifies the geometry of biological time because the variations it triggers are anchored to the physical value
  
